data.description: This sophisticated, four bedroom three and a half bath residence is nestled on quite street with towering mature trees, you are embraced with elegance upon entering the estate, soaring ceilings, gleaming red oak hardwood floors and these are just your views as you enter the home, grand two story foyer brings in remarkable natural light, the sensational open floor plan is perfect for entertaining guests, sophisticated decor with an emphasis on timeless elegance, marvelous gourmet kitchen with shockingly large island, granite counter tops with abundant cabinet and counter space, which boasts incredible palladian windows with newer custom window treatments, a gorgeous neutral brick surround fireplace and creamy white wood detailing.  cabinetry, smooth granite countertops, premium nickel hardware, high-end stainless steel appliances, a butler pantry with a convenient second sink and a pass through overlooking the family room area.   second floor boasts four large bedrooms and ample closet space, luxurious master suite with enormous walk in closet and private glamour bathroom, the full hallway bath also has luxe upgrades including a gleaming onyx vanity, contemporary cabinetry and upscale lighting.  Gather within the expansive lower level light-filled recreation room with plush carpeting and crisp neutral paint; this space is just perfect for entertaining, installed new real hardwood floors in the office and and dining room,  The lower level also features another full bathroom, installed new LVP throughout the entire basement, new Kohler comfort height toilets installed in all bathrooms, all new designer light fixtures, new vanity with marble top and higher end Kohler fixtures installed in master bath and first floor powder room, LED ceiling can throughout the kitchen, custom painted cabinetry in pantry and coffee bar kitchen, LED kichler lighting in office, Schoenbeck crystal chandeliers in foyer, kitchenette and dining room, Decora switches and outlets first and second floor, brand new insulated garage doors with professional genie garage doors and openers in all bays, custom shelving installed for shoes in garage, garage floor epoxied, and sealed 2023 and all walls painted, Hinkley luxury lighting installed exterior of home, new electrolux front load washer and dryer with pedestals substantially sized wet bar, separate laundry room with utilities, and the two large closets provide all of the storage you could ever need.  The Mill Creek Crossing community in Gurnee offers direct access and is just steps from private HOA owned trails, a cross country ski loop and pond incredibly private backyard, professional landscaped grounds, quarter acre lush green lot in the peaceful,  .    and just beyond the backyard is Mill Creek and nothing but a quiet wooded area, newly refinished patio and serene wooded view of the sprawling backyard just steps away from Mill Creek.    This marvelous location is within close proximity to shopping, fantastic dining options, I-94 and nearby theme parks.  Excellent top-rated school districts 50 & 121 featuring Warren Township High School
